reviewText:
The little girl is missing her far away working parents, she wish they can come home to the new year. But year after year, her parents can not come home for many reasons. The pass by train bring her wishes away.  She is looking after her little baby brother and he made her to be strong and growing up...
Touch story, cute kids, also let us know that do not work or live far away with our kids. Nothing is more important than the whole family stay together.
